<br>
This command will put more than one (up to five) chat boxes on your screen. The command is /hitsmode. When you type that in you get the response:<br>
<br>
&lt;my/me/other&gt;&lt;on|off|m2|m3|m4|m5&gt;&lt;x&gt;&lt;y&gt;&lt;count&gt;<br>
&lt;fontsize&gt;&lt;header&gt;&lt;BG&gt;&lt;width&gt;&lt;forcedraw&gt;<br>
<br>
So you need to give an answer for each item within the arrows. Here are what each one means:<br>
My=My attacks, Me=Me getting hit, Other=Other's attacks<br>
on=The messages to to the chat window<br>
off=the messages are filtered out completely<br>
m2 through m5=the messages go to a separate window<br>
<br>
If you choose m2 through m5, then:<br>
&lt;x&gt; and &lt;y&gt; are the screen location (where the new box is)<br>
&lt;count&gt;is how many lines from 1 to 10<br>
&lt;fontsize&gt; of 0, 1, or 2<br>
&lt;header) 1 or 0 to turn on or off header<br>
&lt;bg&gt; 1 or 0 to turn on or off background poly<br>
&lt;width&gt; is the width of the bk poly<br>
&lt;forcedraw&gt; 1 forces the window to draw even if empty<br>
(note= m5 = my attacks, but no other types of messages)<br>
<br>
Taking all this into account, I set up my screen with one <br>
chat box (the normal one, leaving it as it is), a box for <br>
&quot;others hits&quot; (m2), a box for &quot;my hits&quot; (m3), and a box <br>
for &quot;me getting hit&quot; (m5). <br>
<br>
<br>
The following are the commands that you must type in to <br>
get these boxes (recommended on a 1024 x 768 mode view):<br>
<br>
/hitsmode other m2 700 700 8 2 1 1 300 1<br>
/hitsmode my m3 700 550 8 2 1 1 300 1<br>
/hitsmode me m5 700 400 8 2 1 1 300 1<br>
<br>
If someone gives me a web address where I can put a <br>
picture of my screen I will illustrate this for you.<br>
<br>
Try it! You just might like it! I love it!<br>
<br>
Hama <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#202020><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub76.ezboard.com/brandomacts.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=oggarbugg>Oggarbugg</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><b>RA Member<br><font color=blue>Grand master of all things<br> material and immaterial<br> in this world and others.</font></b></span><br>  Posts: 357<br> <font color=#00FFFF>(6/18/02 10:31:26 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub76.ezboard.com/frandomactsfrm17.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=292.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_super_ez.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: /hitsmode Separate your chat and damage screens!!!</span><hr size=1> WooT! I just read this so have not tried it, but Oh, the possibilities!<br>
